#

Balsamic Portobello Burger

25 min
$8.5
450 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

Gluten

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianHigh Fiber

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Course

Tags:

HealthyQuickEasy

Description

A delicious and hearty burger featuring marinated portobello mushrooms, topped with fresh ingredients for a satisfying bite.

Ingredients

  • portobello mushrooms: 2 large
  • whole wheat burger buns: 2
  • fresh spinach: 1 cup
  • tomato slices: 1 medium
  • avocado slices: 1 medium
  • balsamic vinegar: 2 tablespoons
  • olive oil: 1 tablespoon
  • garlic powder: 1 teaspoon
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
